OL,3,CMeghan to expand her As ever brand in
OL,4,CAustralia rather than UK
OL,6,FThe Duchess of Sussex is looking to
OL,7,Fexpand her As ever business venture to
OL,8,FAustralia before she starts selling
OL,9,Fany of her products in the UK.
OL,11,FHarry and Meghan's office has
OL,12,Fconfirmed the couple will visit
OL,13,FAustralia in mid-April.
OL,15,FThe two-to-three-day visit is still
OL,16,Fbeing finalised, but the Sussexes are
OL,17,Flikely to travel to Sydney and
OL,18,FMelbourne as they take part in what
OL,19,Ftheir office called "a number of
OL,20,Fprivate, business, and philanthropic
OL,21,Fengagements."
OL,26,@{D@UOU}D@MO]
