OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773079565
OL,3,CMeghan to expand her As ever brand in
OL,4,CAustralia rather than UK
OL,6,FFor Meghan, the private business
OL,7,Fmeetings will focus on how she might
OL,8,Fexpand her As ever-branded lifestyle
OL,9,Fproducts outside the USA for the first
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FLast week, the Duchess announced she
OL,13,Fhad ended her business venture with
OL,14,FNetflix, which had invested in As ever.
OL,16,FIt's understood she thought the
OL,17,Fstreaming giant was a bad fit for her
OL,18,Fwebsite, which sells items like jam,
OL,19,Frose wine and flower sprinkles, and
OL,20,Fwas being too cautious with its
OL,21,Fexpansion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
