OL,3,CMeghan to expand her As ever brand in
OL,4,CAustralia rather than UK
OL,6,FHarry and Meghan will still work with
OL,7,FNetflix on a 'first-look' basis, which
OL,8,Fgives the media giant first refusal on
OL,9,Fany new production ideas.
OL,11,FHaving decided to go it alone with As
OL,12,Fever, Meghan now wants to test her
OL,13,Fitems in other English-speaking
OL,14,Fcountries, and it seems Australia,
OL,15,Frather than the UK, is the chosen
OL,16,Fmarket.
OL,18,FThe expansion of As ever might also
OL,19,Fsee Meghan selling her items in New
OL,20,FZealand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
