OL,3,CMeghan to expand her As ever brand in
OL,4,CAustralia rather than UK
OL,6,FThe couple's children, Archie and
OL,7,FLilibet, will stay at their home in
OL,8,FCalifornia as they will still be
OL,9,Fattending school.
OL,11,FHarry and Meghan were last in
OL,12,FAustralia in 2018, a few months after
OL,13,Ftheir wedding at Windsor Castle, when
OL,14,Fthey announced Meghan was pregnant
OL,15,Fwith their first child.
OL,17,FThat trip was an official royal tour,
OL,18,Fwhen the couple were still working
OL,19,Fmembers of the Royal Family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
