OL,3,CMeghan to expand her As ever brand in
OL,4,CAustralia rather than UK
OL,6,FIt was much longer and took in
OL,7,FAustralia, Fiji, Tonga and New Zealand.
OL,9,FThis time, they will be travelling as
OL,10,Fprivate citizens with their own
OL,11,Fsecurity team ` although the
OL,12,FAustralian government may have to pick
OL,13,Fup any bills for extra security at
OL,14,Ftheir public events.
OL,16,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,17,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,18,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,19,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson
